1. **World Health Organization (2011).** *Haemoglobin concentrations for the diagnosis of anaemia and assessment of severity.* WHO/NMH/NHD/MNM/11.1.  
   Disponível em: [https://www.who.int/vmnis/indicators/haemoglobin.pdf](https://www.who.int/vmnis/indicators/haemoglobin.pdf)

2. **WHO, UNICEF, UNU (2001).** *Iron deficiency anaemia: assessment, prevention and control.* Geneva: World Health Organization.

3. **WHO (1989).** *Preventing and controlling anaemia through primary health care.* Geneva: WHO.

4. **WHO (2000).** *The management of nutrition in major emergencies.* Geneva: WHO.

5. **CDC (1989).** *Criteria for anaemia in children and childbearing-aged women.* *Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report*, 38(22):400–404.
